      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(3 inline comments)\n\nI have to agree with Nathaniel - if the \"resend request while RPCs are in flight\" patch only landed recently, this patch shouldn't remove the exclusion for server version < 2.5.52.  Am I mistaken, and does this test work correctly for old servers as well?",
